@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((tmp - (tmp + 0.83 + v2 + 0.52)) + (wp.cos(v1 + 0.56) + (v0 + 0.65 / v0 + 0.25)))
    v0 = (wp.cos(tmp) * (0.28 * v0))
    v2 = wp.sin(0.01)
    v2 = v2
